data.text:
FREE SHIPPING

We offer free standard shipping on all product orders. The free shipping method will be the least costly of either UPS Ground Service (1-5 business days delivery) or Mail Priority Mail (1-4 business days delivery).

If you prefer the alternate service that is not the least costly, you can select that service at checkout.

WHEN WILL MY ORDER SHIP?

Our team is committed to excellence. They appreciate the opportunity to prepare your order. You can count on them to flawlessly process your order and get your gear in-transit to you as quickly as possible.

Orders placed before 2:00 PM Time ship the same business day. Orders received on holidays or after 2:00 PM are shipped the next business day. Orders received on weekends or after 2:00 PM on Friday are shipped Monday.
